{"tid":2198431,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前巴塞理療師因非禮女員工入獄4年,巴塞賠償1萬歐元","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T10:59:01.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8bc3f058d3e13b5fe752e5d66ec9be1fae8640","tid":2198431,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/andreajvilloria/status/1304006634331672576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fandreajvilloria%2Fstatus%2F1304006634331672576&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=9ef8bc61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fandreajvilloria%2Fstatus%2F1304006634331672576&h=523bd9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/andreajvilloria/status/1304006634331672576</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年的12月19日,也是最後一次治療中,Jaume Jard&iacute;在按摩中多次觸摸當事人的隱私部位,持續時間達到數分鐘,隨後又觸摸當事人的胸部,期間當事人直接質問Jaume Jard&iacute;這樣的動作是否是必要的,並且在之後心理受到嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n現年52歲的Jaume Jard&iacute;是西班牙運動科學和身體康復界的知名專家,從事該工作長達近30年,曾在巴塞一線隊擔任理療師達7年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19573e8d8352717518e331431ae88f24977bf5f0","tid":2198431,"uid":117037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"球壇之恥疤塞"},{"pid":"13ab65fee2f4955b4f1d72e6a4ff23fb985f1326","tid":2198431,"uid":133545,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"應該都冰山一角 疤狗都無好野 包括球迷"}]}